# AIGOS — Strategic Marketing Blueprint Generator

Stack: Next.js 15, Vercel AI SDK v6, Anthropic Claude, Supabase (DB + realtime), Clerk auth, Railway worker.

## Architecture

The journey is FORM-DRIVEN, not chat-driven. No AI asks questions. No chat-based onboarding.

User flow:
1. Enter URL -> auto-prefill fields
2. Review/edit in GTM Brief Review form
3. Submit -> dispatches deepResearchProgram (corpus + onboarding fields)
4. Corpus completes -> GTM Brief Review form for user to confirm/edit
5. User submits brief -> POST /api/research-v2/orchestrate fans out all six positioning sections
6. Sections commit as drafts in parallel (bounded by ORCHESTRATOR_CONCURRENCY, default 3 -> two waves of three; ~13 min total)
7. Audit Reader renders typed cards per section as each commits
8. All results saved to profile

Fan-out is the canonical flow. The old per-section "Run section" operator click was replaced when /api/research-v2/orchestrate landed. Do not reintroduce sequential single-section dispatch unless explicitly asked.

Research dispatch: Form submit -> POST /api/research-v2/orchestrate (multi-section fan-out) OR POST /api/research-v2/dispatch (single-section, used for corpus + /api/research-v2/rerun-section) -> Railway worker -> Supabase -> realtime to frontend.
Chat sidebar: Post-research editing only (editCard, updateField). Does NOT trigger research.

Pipeline: deepResearchProgram -> positioningMarketCategory -> positioningBuyerICP -> positioningCompetitorLandscape -> positioningVoiceOfCustomer -> positioningDemandIntent -> positioningOfferDiagnostic

## Conventions

- Imports: @/* maps to ./src/* (always absolute)
- UI: shadcn/ui (new-york) + Radix + Tailwind CSS v4. cn() for conditional classes.
- Files: kebab-case. Named exports (not default). Props suffixed with Props.
- All AI calls: @ai-sdk/anthropic directly. Never OpenRouter.
- Zod for all AI outputs and API inputs.

## Gotchas

- id vs run_id: Frontend passes run_id. Query .eq('run_id', id).
- Railway worker (research-worker/) cannot import from src/lib/.
- toUIMessageStreamResponse() requires DefaultChatTransport. Mismatch = silent failure.
- Tool definitions: inputSchema (not parameters), maxOutputTokens (not maxTokens).
- Remove .min()/.max() from Zod numbers in generateObject schemas.
- Read DESIGN.md before any visual/UI work.
